= International Students 

== {{<a href='./SJTU-2019-Master-Programs-in-English-for-International-Students.pdf'> Master & Ph.D. Program</a>}}
To help the international students who have planned to join SJTU for his\/her master\/Ph.D. degree, I hope that these information will be beneficious to you.

=== Background
Shanghai Jiao Tong University (SJTU) is an international institution located in Shanghai, one of the world’s most international cities. Each year we admit students from nearly 80 countries, making the university a rich and diverse learning environment. Currently, SJTU has 60 M.Eng programs and 41 Ph.D. programs for international students.

