=== Admission Criteria
- Non-chinese citizen 
- The physical health status meets the medical examination requirements
- Completed B.Eng degree (Master) & Master degree (Ph.D.)
- Degree Transcript
- Pass the International Examination GRE 320 (total), IELTS 6.0 (overall),
  TOEFL 85 (overall), Cambridge Certificate in Advanced English 176 (overall),
  Cambridge Certificate of Proficiency in English 180 (overall), College
  English Test Band6 510 (overall), NTS GAT General 70%
- Photocopy of Passport
- Passport Photo
- Personal Statement & Research Plan
- 2 Recommendation Letters (The referee must hold a faculty position with an
  associate professor title or higher)

=== Application fees
- 800 RMB (~120USD)

